title: Big-Batch Bacon-Wrapped Meatloaf with Creamy Mash and Brussels Sprouts
description: This recipe comes with larger servings, great for leftovers or big eaters! Hearty cheesy mash and BBQ bacon-wrapped meatloaf is a perfect dinner to have more of!

